comments.body: Category: CraftRoobet Yeti Cash Dash Playable 3D GameWATCH GAMEPLAY HERE:https://youtu.be/nfB5rRf79yY?si=71T_US3QfpAAVKT_I've been brainstorming on how I can incorporate the Yeti Cash dash game and roobet in my clay art in a playable game board for weeks now and it was quite a tedious task. Nonetheless, I enjoyed coming up with ideas with this one and I hope you guys enjoy this one too! Watch the video to see how the gameplay works.Basically it's the same as the Yeti cash dash game towers and you need to choose the correct platform to be able to continue. In playing the game you can move your character Mr. Roo from the starting platform to reach the Yeti King. You can change the arrangement of the platform after each game, just like in the video game , so you can randomize the platforms and try to guess which platform is the correct one.Album Process:https://imgur.com/a/UDNjUiEÂ Roobet username: lucifurBTC ADDRESS: bc1qqha8dnvmsu736pc0jaq90hgz977lnkll83c9eh
